flowchart TD
    A[main.asm receives command] --> B{command}
    B -->|info file| C[info.asm]
    B -->|mitigations file| M[mitigations.asm]

    C --> D[filemap.asm openat fstat mmap]
    M --> D
    D --> E[elf64.asm validate ELF64 x86_64 little-endian]

    E -->|info| F[report_text.asm ELF info]
    E -->|mitigations| G[phdr.asm iterate program headers]
    G --> H[regions.asm store executable PT_LOAD + PF_X records]
    G --> I[phdr_summary mitigation facts]
    H --> J[report_text.asm mitigation report]
    I --> J

    F --> K[filemap.asm munmap cleanup]
    J --> K
    K --> L[exit with stable status]

    E -->|invalid| X[errors.asm diagnostic]
    D -->|file error| X
    G -->|malformed phdr| X
    X --> K
